# Preset 06: Streaming — tokens arrive incrementally
# Simulates LLM streaming: tokens fed one at a time to setText()

<stream>
<token>The</token>
<token> quick</token>
<token> **brown</token>
<token>** fox</token>
<token> jumps</token>
<token> over</token>
<token> the</token>
<token> `lazy</token>
<token> dog`</token>
<token>.</token>
</stream>

<full>
The quick **brown** fox jumps over the `lazy dog`.
</full>

---EXPECT---
# The final render of incremental setText() should match full-text render
stream_matches_full: true
contains: brown
contains: lazy dog
